videos.description: On a fast break, Kenrich Williams hits Desmond Bane with a long pass and Bane finishes with a jam.
videos.headline: TCU's Bane throws it down

videos.description: West Virginia's James Bolden drills a 3-pointer then hits a jumper on the next Mountaineer possession to even the score at 14-14.
videos.headline: Bolden's back-to-back buckets tie game

videos.description: Kouat Noi throws down a slam with power off an inbounds pass.
videos.headline: TCU's Noi hammers it home

videos.description: Sagaba Konate and Esa Ahmad come up with back-to-back blocks on TCU.
videos.headline: West Virginia brings TCU the stuffing

videos.description: Desmond Bane knocks down the prayer from deep as the shot clock winds down.
videos.headline: Bane hits from way downtown for TCU
